WEBVTT

00:01:33.319 --> 00:01:34.439
You're back.

00:01:38.840 --> 00:01:39.599
Leng Qingqiu.

00:01:40.920 --> 00:01:42.480
Why did you come here?

00:01:43.200 --> 00:01:44.640
I came to chat with you.

00:01:44.719 --> 00:01:45.519
Is that not okay?

00:01:48.840 --> 00:01:49.920
That batch of medicine...

00:01:49.920 --> 00:01:51.319
I've already destroyed it.

00:01:51.599 --> 00:01:52.400
I know.

00:01:53.040 --> 00:01:54.920
Didn't you hate me the most before?

00:01:54.920 --> 00:01:56.120
You'd run away when you saw me.

00:01:56.400 --> 00:01:57.680
And now you're...

00:01:58.000 --> 00:01:59.799
What are you doing here in the middle of the night?

00:01:59.799 --> 00:02:00.599
Are you crazy?

00:02:00.599 --> 00:02:02.599
Didn't you use to wish I'd look at you more?

00:02:03.120 --> 00:02:04.480
Now I've come to you.

00:02:04.840 --> 00:02:06.840
Why pretend to be pure and chaste?

00:02:07.040 --> 00:02:07.840
Hypocrite.

00:02:10.439 --> 00:02:12.599
I have to find a way to cut ties with her.

00:02:20.879 --> 00:02:22.319
Well, since you don't want to leave,

00:02:23.120 --> 00:02:24.400
drink this.

00:02:24.680 --> 00:02:25.680
Liven things up for me.

00:02:29.240 --> 00:02:31.039
You, Leng Qingqiu, have always been proud.

00:02:32.000 --> 00:02:33.039
First, you never drink.

00:02:33.039 --> 00:02:34.080
Second, you don't take threats.

00:02:34.319 --> 00:02:36.280
It's always been me trying to please you.

00:02:36.280 --> 00:02:37.280
I don't believe

00:02:37.280 --> 00:02:38.840
you can take this humiliation now.

00:02:39.680 --> 00:02:40.479
Lu Chengwen,

00:02:41.840 --> 00:02:43.039
what do you mean?

00:02:48.400 --> 00:02:49.280
I can't feel sorry for her.

00:02:50.039 --> 00:02:51.840
I must not be fooled by her puppy eyes.

00:02:52.240 --> 00:02:53.520
I can't get tangled up with her.

00:02:55.120 --> 00:02:56.400
You can't drink it, right?

00:02:57.039 --> 00:02:58.000
Just leave.

00:03:11.319 --> 00:03:12.400
I can't be soft-hearted.

00:03:26.639 --> 00:03:27.439
Enough.

00:03:28.319 --> 00:03:30.000
If you can't drink, don't pretend.

00:03:30.719 --> 00:03:31.919
You can scold me

00:03:32.199 --> 00:03:33.479
or hit me a few times.

00:03:35.919 --> 00:03:36.719
Just go.

00:03:39.840 --> 00:03:40.599
What are you doing?

00:03:41.840 --> 00:03:42.639
Leng Qingqiu,

00:03:42.800 --> 00:03:44.039
calm down, okay?

00:03:46.240 --> 00:03:48.000
You are a woman with your own career,

00:03:48.000 --> 00:03:49.319
an excellent woman.

00:03:49.719 --> 00:03:50.840
There's no need to waste all your time

00:03:50.840 --> 00:03:52.400
on a scumbag like me.

00:03:53.520 --> 00:03:55.319
But you chased me for three years.

00:03:56.000 --> 00:03:56.639
Why?

00:03:56.639 --> 00:03:58.639
Now that I've agreed,

00:03:59.039 --> 00:04:00.840
you want me to leave you.

00:04:05.840 --> 00:04:07.000
Because...

00:04:07.800 --> 00:04:08.840
I'm tired.

00:04:08.840 --> 00:04:09.840
I'm annoyed.

00:04:12.120 --> 00:04:13.319
I'm turned off.

00:04:22.839 --> 00:04:23.639
Fine.

00:04:26.279 --> 00:04:27.319
Then I'll go.

00:04:39.680 --> 00:04:40.639
Bastard.

00:04:43.519 --> 00:04:45.639
As long as you feel better scolding me.

00:04:46.199 --> 00:04:47.240
Hurry up and leave.

00:04:52.639 --> 00:04:53.839
Do you

00:04:54.800 --> 00:04:56.319
hate me a lot now?

00:04:59.800 --> 00:05:00.600
Yeah.

00:05:03.680 --> 00:05:04.680
How is that possible?

00:05:05.279 --> 00:05:06.879
Such a lovely and touching beauty,

00:05:07.000 --> 00:05:08.279
only a crazy person wouldn't like her.

00:05:12.199 --> 00:05:13.480
I knew it.

00:05:47.519 --> 00:05:48.600
What was I doing just now?

00:05:48.680 --> 00:05:50.079
I almost fell for it.

00:05:52.480 --> 00:05:53.240
This woman

00:05:53.240 --> 00:05:54.319
is absolutely crazy.

00:06:02.480 --> 00:06:04.120
Trying to drink with such a low tolerance.

00:06:27.399 --> 00:06:29.120
I'm going to sleep in another room.

00:06:29.439 --> 00:06:31.439
Don't try to blame me when you wake up tomorrow.

00:06:49.199 --> 00:06:51.199
Everything needs video evidence.

00:06:51.480 --> 00:06:52.560
I'm

00:06:52.560 --> 00:06:53.600
recording right now.

00:06:54.480 --> 00:06:55.879
Last night,

00:06:55.879 --> 00:06:57.279
I slept outside.

00:06:57.800 --> 00:06:59.680
I just came in from outside.

00:07:00.079 --> 00:07:01.839
I didn't take advantage of you.

00:07:11.920 --> 00:07:12.720
Lu Chengwen

00:07:15.240 --> 00:07:17.040
You finally showed your true colors.

00:07:17.240 --> 00:07:18.319
You little pervert.

00:07:19.199 --> 00:07:20.480
What do you mean, little pervert?

00:07:20.480 --> 00:07:22.600
I just took a video to keep as evidence.

00:07:22.800 --> 00:07:24.240
I didn't do anything out of line.

00:07:24.240 --> 00:07:25.839
Our relationship has always been pure.

00:07:27.439 --> 00:07:28.240
Right?

00:07:28.839 --> 00:07:30.279
I slept in another room last night.

00:07:37.439 --> 00:07:38.240
Really?

00:07:38.839 --> 00:07:39.800
That's good.

00:07:40.480 --> 00:07:42.839
Shouldn't she think I got her drunk on purpose,

00:07:43.199 --> 00:07:44.800
and then tried to take advantage of her?

00:07:45.000 --> 00:07:46.920
And now I'm taking pictures of her

00:07:47.199 --> 00:07:48.439
to blackmail her later?

00:07:48.439 --> 00:07:49.600
If you really dare to do that,

00:07:49.720 --> 00:07:51.079
I'll kill you.

00:07:58.720 --> 00:08:00.319
If you're going to keep standing in the way,

00:08:00.439 --> 00:08:01.439
then please

00:08:01.879 --> 00:08:03.040
help me grab that.

00:08:19.040 --> 00:08:21.040
This Leng Qingqiu seems pretty nice.

00:08:21.439 --> 00:08:23.319
She's not that unreasonable after all.

00:08:24.800 --> 00:08:25.600
You brat!

00:08:26.439 --> 00:08:28.040
Did you do something bad again?

00:08:42.080 --> 00:08:42.879
Mom!

00:08:47.679 --> 00:08:48.440
Mom,

00:08:48.440 --> 00:08:49.480
why are you here too?

00:08:50.279 --> 00:08:51.480
Why am I here?

00:08:51.480 --> 00:08:53.320
If I didn't come, you'd keep doing bad things!

00:08:53.320 --> 00:08:54.440
You little brat!

00:08:54.639 --> 00:08:55.200
Last night,

00:08:55.200 --> 00:08:56.879
how could you do that to Qingqiu?

00:08:57.120 --> 00:08:57.320
Mom,

00:08:57.320 --> 00:08:58.200
listen to me.

00:08:58.200 --> 00:08:58.639
Explain?

00:08:58.639 --> 00:08:59.240
I...

00:08:59.639 --> 00:09:00.639
I didn't do anything last night!

00:09:00.639 --> 00:09:01.039
I...

00:09:01.039 --> 00:09:01.919
I want you to explain!

00:09:02.600 --> 00:09:03.320
I want you to explain!

00:09:03.320 --> 00:09:04.120
Mom!

00:09:05.440 --> 00:09:06.240
Qingqiu,

00:09:06.399 --> 00:09:08.480
it was wrong of Chengwen to get you drunk.

00:09:08.519 --> 00:09:09.600
I'll beat him up for you.

00:09:10.120 --> 00:09:10.919
Also,

00:09:11.000 --> 00:09:12.080
he has to take responsibility for you.

00:09:12.440 --> 00:09:14.600
Our families will discuss the wedding properly.

00:09:14.840 --> 00:09:15.600
This porridge is good.

00:09:15.600 --> 00:09:16.320
Have some.

00:09:16.320 --> 00:09:16.919
It'll help you sober up.

00:09:16.919 --> 00:09:17.720
Thank you, Auntie.

00:09:26.120 --> 00:09:27.440
You still have the nerve to eat?

00:09:28.120 --> 00:09:28.799
No,

00:09:28.799 --> 00:09:29.600
Mom,

00:09:29.600 --> 00:09:30.840
let me serve you some.

00:09:31.120 --> 00:09:32.039
You have some too.

00:09:32.200 --> 00:09:33.080
What's wrong, son?

00:09:33.200 --> 00:09:34.320
Did you change your personality today?

00:09:35.000 --> 00:09:35.679
Well,

00:09:35.679 --> 00:09:37.200
I haven't seen you for days.

00:09:37.240 --> 00:09:38.200
I missed you.

00:09:38.840 --> 00:09:40.000
He's quite filial.

00:09:40.200 --> 00:09:41.399
You little brat.

00:09:41.399 --> 00:09:42.080
I'll eat later.

00:09:42.080 --> 00:09:43.440
Qingqiu,

00:09:43.600 --> 00:09:44.639
you two have a good chat.

00:09:44.720 --> 00:09:46.440
The servants are still cooking in the kitchen.

00:09:46.440 --> 00:09:47.799
I'll go see how it's going.

00:09:48.000 --> 00:09:48.240
Yeah.

00:09:48.240 --> 00:09:48.600
Okay,

00:09:48.600 --> 00:09:49.440
Auntie.

00:10:17.039 --> 00:10:18.799
How can there be such a beautiful woman?

00:10:19.200 --> 00:10:20.240
Just watching her eat

00:10:20.240 --> 00:10:21.720
is a pleasure.

00:10:22.639 --> 00:10:23.840
What am I thinking?

00:10:24.039 --> 00:10:25.519
I need to get her away from me quickly.

00:10:26.320 --> 00:10:27.320
So weird.

00:10:28.039 --> 00:10:30.080
I used to feel disgusted when he called me beautiful.

00:10:30.600 --> 00:10:32.440
Why does it sound so pleasing today?

00:10:32.840 --> 00:10:33.840
But why is he now

00:10:33.840 --> 00:10:35.399
always trying to distance himself from me?

00:10:41.799 --> 00:10:42.600
Lu Chengwen.

00:10:46.120 --> 00:10:46.799
Just now,

00:10:46.799 --> 00:10:48.120
about Auntie mentioning marriage,

00:10:48.279 --> 00:10:49.200
what do you think?

00:10:51.039 --> 00:10:52.120
About the marriage,

00:10:52.399 --> 00:10:53.480
I didn't think much of it.

00:10:53.720 --> 00:10:54.519
Don't worry,

00:10:54.879 --> 00:10:55.639
I will

00:10:55.799 --> 00:10:56.720
help you turn it down.

00:10:57.720 --> 00:10:59.279
Why don't you want to get married?

00:11:00.440 --> 00:11:01.679
Do you like me?

00:11:02.120 --> 00:11:02.879
I...

00:11:02.879 --> 00:11:04.120
Of course I don't.

00:11:04.240 --> 00:11:05.039
Exactly.

00:11:05.440 --> 00:11:06.840
You don't even like me,

00:11:06.840 --> 00:11:08.279
so why would I marry you?

00:11:08.879 --> 00:11:09.919
Then why don't you

00:11:09.919 --> 00:11:11.240
keep trying a little longer?

00:11:12.639 --> 00:11:13.080
What's wrong?

00:11:13.080 --> 00:11:14.519
Do I look that cheap?

00:11:16.399 --> 00:11:17.679
Did you

00:11:17.919 --> 00:11:19.200
fall for someone else?

00:11:20.840 --> 00:11:22.080
Making me report everything,

00:11:22.320 --> 00:11:23.600
I'm not your subordinate.

00:11:23.840 --> 00:11:24.679
So annoying.

00:11:32.200 --> 00:11:32.840
Yeah.

00:11:32.840 --> 00:11:34.120
I fell for someone else.

00:11:35.639 --> 00:11:36.440
Hello?

00:11:36.639 --> 00:11:37.600
Babe Xue Jiao!

00:11:38.080 --> 00:11:39.840
You little tease.

00:11:39.840 --> 00:11:41.039
What do you need from Big bro?

00:11:41.519 --> 00:11:42.679
Don't use such a disgusting tone.

00:11:42.679 --> 00:11:43.840
The press conference is starting soon.

00:11:43.840 --> 00:11:44.600
Come over quickly.

00:11:45.679 --> 00:11:47.120
Missed Big bro, huh?

00:11:47.200 --> 00:11:47.639
Hahaha.

00:11:47.639 --> 00:11:48.240
Alright.

00:11:48.240 --> 00:11:49.200
Just wait.

00:11:49.240 --> 00:11:50.600
Big bro will be right there.

00:11:53.600 --> 00:11:54.399
Weird.

00:11:55.000 --> 00:11:56.480
Why am I angry?

00:11:56.840 --> 00:11:59.200
I hope he doesn't think I care about him.

00:11:59.279 --> 00:11:59.960
But

00:12:00.159 --> 00:12:01.840
how could he change his mind so suddenly?

00:12:02.120 --> 00:12:02.600
Scumbag.

00:12:03.120 --> 00:12:04.000
Qingqiu,

00:12:05.440 --> 00:12:06.320
what's wrong?

00:12:06.840 --> 00:12:07.639
What?

00:12:07.720 --> 00:12:08.799
Trying to coax me?

00:12:09.720 --> 00:12:11.320
I won't forgive you.

00:12:11.600 --> 00:12:12.639
I'm fine.

00:12:12.720 --> 00:12:13.879
I'm just afraid

00:12:13.879 --> 00:12:16.240
of delaying you from seeing your sweetheart.

00:12:17.679 --> 00:12:19.039
You're so smart.

00:12:19.080 --> 00:12:20.240
You saw right through me.

00:12:20.240 --> 00:12:20.840
Alright.

00:12:20.840 --> 00:12:22.039
Take your time eating.

00:12:22.039 --> 00:12:23.120
I won't keep you company anymore.